Plasma_Punch.help: You charge up your plasma gauntlets to deliver a powerful punch to your target. This causes smashing and energy damage. It also has a chance to knock your target down.
Plasma_Punch.shortHelp: Melee, Moderate DMG(Smashing/Energy), Chance for Knockdown (Foe)

Plasma_Smasher.shortHelp: Melee, High DMG(Smashing/Energy), Chance for Stun (Foe)

Plasma_Blast.help: You charge up your plasma gauntlets, firing a small blast of plasma at a single target. The target suffers energy damage and is set ablaze, suffering additional fire damage over time. The target may also be knocked down by the attack.
Plasma_Blast.shortHelp: Ranged, Moderate DMG(Energy), Minor DoT(Fire), Chance for Knockdown (Foe)

Plasma_Grenade.help: You throw a plasma grenade at a single target. This grenade explodes into a field of plasma which burns any targets caught within the field.

Summon_Battle_Orb.help: You summon a Battle Orb to assist you. The Battle Orb that arrives may be one of three varieties.

IDF_Armor.help: Your IDF battle armor grants you improved resistance to all forms of damage.
